short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Default search extension that enhances the music search experience by intelligently identifying music-related keywords

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When users search for music or music artist-related terms, they are provided with quick access to search directly on the relevant music site. The primary focus of this extension is to cater to the music search needs of music lovers and anyone who enjoys listening to music.

Learn more: https://www.musicsearchapp.net/
